    "## Overview\n",
    "\n",
    "This section analyzes salary and compensation patterns in 2024 job postings using the Lightcast dataset. The goal is to understand how salaries vary across occupations, industries, locations, employment types, remote work arrangements, and AI-related skills.\n",
    "\n",
    "Because salary information is not available for every job posting, this analysis focuses on records with valid salary values greater than zero when comparing salary outcomes.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Load Prepared Data\n",
    "\n",
    "This section loads the prepared analysis tables created in the data preparation step. The salary analysis page uses these saved Parquet files directly instead of rebuilding relational tables and AI classifications."
